WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:55.760 --> 00:00:57.180
Bear, are you sick, or what?

00:00:58.497 --> 00:01:00.177
Then I'll be your doctor!

00:01:01.880 --> 00:01:04.940
It's a good thing I came! I know how to treat
a patient!

00:01:09.980 --> 00:01:11.680
Well, my dear, let's give you 
a checkup!

00:01:17.367 --> 00:01:18.087
OK, OK, OK.

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:22.320
Doesn't look so good.

00:01:23.716 --> 00:01:25.236
So that's the problem.

00:01:25.620 --> 00:01:27.840
Yes, it is a complicated case.

00:01:29.640 --> 00:01:31.420
The only thing that will help you is...

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:34.760
Some bed rest!

00:01:40.313 --> 00:01:42.153
Lay down, my dear, and rest!

00:01:47.200 --> 00:01:51.680
Let's have some tea with raspberries!

00:01:53.240 --> 00:01:55.560
Medicine has to be tasty and sweet.

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:27.800
And you… don't get out of bed!

00:02:50.896 --> 00:02:52.336
Did you get out of bed?

00:02:54.920 --> 00:02:56.040
And still you’re sick?

00:03:00.299 --> 00:03:02.779
Well, all right. Let's check you out.

00:03:05.320 --> 00:03:07.040
OK. It seems OK...

00:03:07.146 --> 00:03:08.746
It's all right here too.

00:03:15.948 --> 00:03:17.948
Well, you are seriously sick!

00:03:19.520 --> 00:03:23.080
You urgently need a very restful bed rest!

00:04:13.160 --> 00:04:17.680
You were sick yesterday. You are sick today.
Are you not tired of it?

00:04:20.760 --> 00:04:25.040
OK, OK. You talked me into it. I'll check
you out.

00:04:39.440 --> 00:04:42.680
You get the most restful of all the bed rests!

00:04:43.480 --> 00:04:45.600
I'll go get the medicine and be right back!

00:05:10.920 --> 00:05:13.360
Hurry! It's an emergency!

00:05:14.440 --> 00:05:17.600
Wow! Wow! Wow! Wow!

00:05:22.200 --> 00:05:26.800
And one! And two! And one! And three!

00:05:32.049 --> 00:05:33.889
And two! And three! And one!

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:47.960
Faster! Faster!

00:05:50.003 --> 00:05:51.443
Go faster! Go faster!

00:05:53.040 --> 00:05:54.520
Stop now!

00:06:30.880 --> 00:06:33.000
I do know how to treat a patient!

